h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of the use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Settings|guide:_ShowApplicationPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "User Management" sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Role* link.
* [Show Landing Page of Role|guide:ShowRoleActionService].
* Select a Line-Item from grid view.
* Click "Edit" button from tool bar.
* [Open Role in Edit Mode|guide:SelectRoleActionService].
* User must enter valid input to update.
* Click "Update" button from tool bar.
* Update *Role*.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Update Role" privilege.
* Follow rules of validation:
{table}
*Field* | *Input Type* | *Data Type* | *Rules*
Name | Text Box | Alpha Numeric | Required & Unique
{table}

* Match expected version before updating a *Role*.

h4. Process:
* Update selected *Role*.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Update selected *Role* into grid-view.
** Show success message.
** Reset the field for next inputs.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].
